{"words":[{"word":"brant","count":4},{"word":"ms","count":3},{"word":"lenore","count":3},{"word":"world","count":3},{"word":"ha","count":2},{"word":"old","count":2},{"word":"jokes","count":2},{"word":"listen","count":2},{"word":"captain","count":2},{"word":"ah","count":2},{"word":"letters","count":2},{"word":"every","count":2},{"word":"laughter","count":2},{"word":"reason","count":2},{"word":"live","count":2},{"word":"righteous","count":1},{"word":"join","count":1},{"word":"pilgrimage","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"truth","count":1},{"word":"laugh","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"teasing","count":1},{"word":"clown","count":1},{"word":"sorry","count":1},{"word":"miss","count":1},{"word":"man","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"bet","count":1},{"word":"hundred","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"twenty-one","count":1},{"word":"short","count":1},{"word":"starting","count":1},{"word":"sweat","count":1},{"word":"hang","count":1},{"word":"debt","count":1},{"word":"collectors","count":1},{"word":"professional","count":1},{"word":"financial","count":1},{"word":"advisor","count":1},{"word":"whatever","count":1},{"word":"owes","count":1},{"word":"valid","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"proper","count":1},{"word":"iou","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"something-something","count":1},{"word":"archive","count":1},{"word":"sanctuary","count":1},{"word":"affairs","count":1},{"word":"bureau","count":1},{"word":"sent","count":1},{"word":"sympathy","count":1},{"word":"applied","count":1},{"word":"order's","count":1},{"word":"aid","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"single","count":1},{"word":"penny","count":1},{"word":"words","count":1},{"word":"meant","count":1},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"girl","count":1},{"word":"survived","count":1},{"word":"straight","count":1},{"word":"pleasure","count":1},{"word":"carefully","count":1},{"word":"grab","count":1},{"word":"unhappy","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"direct","count":1},{"word":"squarely","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"troupe","count":1},{"word":"fools","count":1},{"word":"tasked","count":1},{"word":"bringing","count":1},{"word":"person","count":1},{"word":"sad","count":1},{"word":"problem","count":1},{"word":"claims","count":1},{"word":"reach","count":1},{"word":"corner","count":1},{"word":"clearly","count":1},{"word":"missed","count":1},{"word":"blame","count":1},{"word":"pure","count":1},{"word":"soul","count":1},{"word":"naive","count":1},{"word":"fault","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"heart","count":1},{"word":"kinder","count":1},{"word":"saved","count":1},{"word":"andreas","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"If you're all so righteous, why don't you join the pilgrimage yourselves!","quest_name":"Through the Sea Thou Break","quest_id":114000026},{"text":"Ha... Haha... Truth... Don't make me laugh...","quest_name":"Through the Sea Thou Break","quest_id":114000026},{"text":"Stop teasing her, you old clown.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"I'm sorry, Miss. This old man made a bet to tell a hundred jokes in a day. He's still twenty-one jokes short and starting to sweat, ha!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Hang on... Are you one of those debt collectors? Listen, I'm a professional financial advisor! Whatever Captain Brant owes you, it's not valid without a proper IOU!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Ah, I remember now! You must be Ms. Lenore from the something-something Archive of the Sanctuary Affairs Bureau, right? You sent me sympathy letters after I applied for the Order's aid.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"They didn't give me a single penny, but your words back then meant the world. Thank you.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Ah... I see what this is all about. The girl survived, but can't think straight.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"With pleasure!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Now, listen to me carefully, Ms. Lenore—I want you to grab every unhappy thought you've got... and direct it squarely at Captain Brant!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Brant said this himself: \"We are the Troupe of Fools, tasked with bringing laughter to the world. If even one person is still sad, then that's on me!\"","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"All the more reason it's a Brant Problem. He claims laughter should reach every corner of the world. Well, clearly it missed yours!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Ms. Lenore, I don't blame a pure soul for being naive. And I won't fault a kind heart for not being kinder.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"If you need a reason to live, let it be this: Your letters once saved me. I, Andreas, hope you'll live on.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002}]}